items.title: West Nile virus detected in UK mosquitoes for first time
items.description: A UK Health Security Agency spokesperson said the risk to the general public is "very low".

items.title: Ukrainian ex-top official shot dead outside Madrid school
items.description: Andriy Portnov, 51, had just dropped his children off when he was attacked.

items.title: X restricted in Tanzania after police targeted by hackers
items.description: After being compromised, explicit images and misinformation were shared on the police's account.

items.title: Canada in talks with US to join Trump's Golden Dome defence system
items.description: PM Mark Carney's office says there are "active discussions" on the Golden Dome, but it's too early to say how Canada would join or pay in.
